(\theta + 1)/3
p(x \mid \theta)
p(x \mid \theta) = {n \choose x}  \theta^x (1 - \theta)^{n-x} 
p(x \mid (\theta + 1)/3) = {100 \choose 58} \left(\frac{\theta + 1}{3}\right)^{58} \left(1 - \frac{\theta + 1}{3}\right)^{100-58} 
