 L(\theta) = \binom{100}{58}\left(\frac{\theta+1}{3}\right)^{58} \left(1-\frac{\theta+1}{3}\right)^{100-58}. 
\dfrac{d}{d\theta}L(\theta)=0
\dfrac{d}{d\theta}\log L(\theta)=0
